     H            Y.                                    1
     F** UEXR15 ***************************************************
     F*  ADJUST FIL1024A AND OUT TO FIL1024B                      *
     F*  J.W    2019.11.21                                        *
     F*  --------------------                                     *
     F*  FUNCTION: PUT " TO THE BEGIN/END OF EACH DATALINE        *
     F*  EX.     : IN: /ABC, XYZ/   ---> OUT: "/ABC, XYZ/"        *
     F*************************************************************
     FFIL1024AIF  E                    DISK
     FFIL1024BO   E                    DISK
      *
     E                    TBA      1024  1
     E                    TBB      1024  1
      ***********************************************
      * MAIN
      ***********************************************
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     READ FIL1024A                 98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C                     MOVEAFLD01A    TBA
     C                     Z-ADD1025      IX      30
      * GET END POSITION
     C                     DO   1024
     C                     SUB  1         IX
      *
     C           IX        IFEQ 0
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           TBA,IX    IFNE *BLANK
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           IX        ADD  1         IY      30
     C                     MOVE '"'       TBA,IY
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
